:"textmodule","body":[{"node":"title","body":[{"node":"text","body":"Engine Oil and Filter - Renew DF4; DG4"}]},{"node":"text","body":"\r\n"},{"node":"ul","body":[{"node":"li","body":[{"node":"p","body":[{"node":"link","body":[{"node":"text","body":"Engine Oil and Filter Renew"}],"target-id":"90071993412025611-2","target-base-id":"864615691"}]}]}],"type":"disc"}],"metadata":{"ModelsTaxonomyLink":"DG4; DF4","MarketsTaxonomyLink":"All"},"type":"TextModule"},{"node":"textmodule","body":[{"node":"title","body":[{"node":"text","body":"Coolant Replacement - Filling DF4; DG4"}]},{"node":"text","body":"\r\n"},{"node":"ul","body":[{"node":"li","body":[{"node":"p","body":[{"node":"link","body":[{"node":"text","body":"Coolant Replacement - Filling"}],"target-id":"126100790388914059-2","target-base-id":"822540171"}]}]}],"type":"disc"}],"metadata":{"ModelsTaxonomyLink":"DG4; DF4","MarketsTaxonomyLink":"All"},"type":"TextModule"},{"node":"textmodule","body":[{"node":"title","body":[{"node":"text","body":"Side Panels DF4; DG4"}]},{"node":"text","body":"\r\n"},{"node":"ul","body":[{"node":"li","body":[{"node":"p","body":[{"node":"link","body":[{"node":"text","body":"Side Panels"}],"target-id":"81064796895057291-2","target-base-id":"3602388363"}]}]}],"type":"disc"}],"metadata":{"ModelsTaxonomyLink":"DG4; DF4","MarketsTaxonomyLink":"All"},"type":"TextModule"},{"node":"textmodule","body":[{"node":"title","body":[{"node":"text","body":"Fuel Tank Installation D74; DF4; DG4; DR4; DS4"}]},{"node":"text","body":"\r\n"},{"node":"ul","body":[{"node":"li","body":[{"node":"p","body":[{"node":"link","body":[{"node":"text","body":"Fuel Tank - Installation"}],"target-id":"99079192589201035-2","target-base-id":"787050123"}]}]}],"type":"dash"},{"node":"text","body":" "}],"metadata":{"ModelsTaxonomyLink":"DS4; DR4; D74; DG4; DF4","MarketsTaxonomyLink":"All"},"type":"TextModule"},{"node":"image","body":[],"type":"svg"},{"node":"image","body":[],"type":"png"},{"node":"image","body":[],"type":"svg"},{"node":"image","body":[],"type":"svg"},{"node":"image","body":[],"type":"svg"},{"node":"image","body":[],"type":"svg"},{"node":"image","body":[],"type":"svg"},{"node":"image","body":[],"type":"svg"},{"node":"image","body":[],"type":"svg"}],"ancestors":["1342357259"],"parent":"1342357259","lastUpdate":"2020-02-17T11:29:42.000Z","metadata":{"products":"DG4; DF4","markets":["All"],"_id":"66705ade9772673c90ccd833"},"search":["Engine - Installation","Make sure the motorcycle is stabilised and adequately supported.","A correctly supported motorcycle will help prevent it from falling.","An unstable motorcycle may fall, causing injury to the operator or damage to the motorcycle.","Prior to fitting the engine, check to ensure that the brake line is attached to the ABS modulator bracket as shown in the following illustration. Rectify if necessary.","ABS brake line","Retaining clips","ABS modulator bracket","Attach the brake lines to the brake line tidy.","Brake line from ABS modulator to front master cylinder. ","Brake line from ABS modulator to front brake caliper","Brake line tidy","Locate the engine to the frame aligning the engine mounting points with the corresponding positions on the frame.","Install the engine mounting bolts and the spacer to the lower crankcase mounting as noted during removal, do not fit the nuts or washers at this stage.","Stage 1","Insert the cylinder head left hand front mounting bolt with washer between the bolt and the frame.","Insert the cylinder head right hand front mounting bolt fit a new lock nut but not fully tighten at this stage.","Fit the spacer between the crankcase and the frame on the right hand side. Insert the crankcase rear lower mounting bolt from the right hand side. Do not fit the washer and new lock nut at this stage.","Insert the crankcase rear upper mounting bolt from the right hand side. Do not fit the washer and new lock nut at this stage.","Insert the cylinder head rear mounting bolt from the right hand side. Do not fit the washer and new lock nut at this stage.","Stage 2","Partially withdraw the crankcase rear lower mounting bolt and tighten the frame adjuster to ","5 Nm"," using ","service tool T3880377",". Refit the bolt and washer.","Partially withdraw the crankcase rear upper mounting bolt and tighten the frame adjuster to ","5 Nm"," using ","service tool T3880377",". Refit the bolt and washer.","Counter hold the cylinder head front right hand cylinder head mounting nut and tighten the bolt to ","24 Nm",".","Withdraw the cylinder head left hand mounting bolt and tighten the frame adjuster to ","5 Nm"," using ","service tool T3880377",".","Withdraw the cylinder head rear mounting bolt and tighten the frame adjuster to ","5 Nm"," using ","service tool T3880377",".","Fit the washer and a new lock nut to the crankcase lower rear mounting bolt. Counter hold the bolt and tighten the nut to ","80 Nm",".","Fit the washer and a new lock nut to the crankcase upper rear mounting bolt. Counter hold the bolt and tighten the nut to ","80 Nm",".","Fit a new lock nut to the cylinder head front right hand mounting bolt. Counter hold the nut and tighten the bolt to ","105 Nm",".","Fit the washer and a new lock nut to the cylinder head front left hand mounting bolt. Counter hold the nut and tighten the bolt to ","105 Nm",".","Fit the washer and a new lock nut to the cylinder head rear mounting bolt. Counter hold the nut and tighten the bolt to ","105 Nm",".","Lower rear crankcase adjuster","Upper rear crankcase adjuster","Left hand cylinder head frame adjuster","Rear cylinder head frame adjuster","Swinging arm adjuster","Stage 3","While supporting the swinging arm, remove the swinging arm spindle and partially insert it from the right hand side. Tighten the frame adjuster to ","6 Nm",".","While supporting the swinging arm, remove the swinging arm spindle and fully insert it with the washer from the left hand side.","Fit the washer and a new lock nut to the swinging arm spindle. Counter hold the nut and tighten the spindle to ","110 Nm","Refit the coolant hose to the thermostat housing and secure using ","service tool T3880207",".","Refit the throttle body (see ","Throttle Body - Installation",").","Refit the clutch cable (see ","Clutch Cable - Installation",").","Refit the crankcase breather hose.","Reconnect the engine earth strap, tightening the fixing to ","6 Nm",".","Route the starter motor cable, crankshaft position sensor and gear position sensor cables as noted during removal. Tighten the cable guide fixings to ","4 Nm",".","Connect the electrical connectors as follows:","Gear position sensor,","Crankshaft position sensor,","Oil pressure switch.","Refit the starter motor cable to the solenoid, tighten the fixing to ","4 Nm",".","Gear position sensor connector","Crankshaft position sensor connector","Starter motor cable","Starter motor solenoid","Refit the brake fluid reservoir, tighten the new fixing to ","3 Nm",".","Refit the drive chain to the front sprocket and adjust (see ","Final Drive Chain Adjustment",").","Attach the alternator harness to the coolant expansion tank mounting, fit the inner cover and tighten its fixings to ","7 Nm",".","Fixings","Harness clip","Alternator harness","Refit the coolant expansion tank to its mountings and tighten the new lock nuts to ","3 Nm",".","Fixings","Coolant expansion tank","Carefully refit the swinging arm pivot cover on the left hand side of the frame.","Fit the sprocket cover and evenly and progressively tighten the fixings to ","9 Nm",".","Refit the swinging arm pivot cover to the left hand side of the frame.","Refit the left hand control plate and tighten its fixings to ","25 Nm",".","Fixings","Control plate","Cover","Refit the left and right hand heel guards and tighten their fixings to ","7 Nm",".","Fixings","Heel guard (left hand side)","Connect the following electrical connectors:","Coolant temperature sensor;","Fuel injectors;","Spark plug leads.","Perform the following operations:","Radiator - Installation","Exhaust Intermediate and Header Pipes - Installation","Cradle Assemblies - Installation","Engine Oil and Filter Renew","Coolant Replacement - Filling","Side Panels","Fuel Tank - Installation"],"viewCount":0,"infoType":"InfoType08","createdAt":"2024-06-17T15:48:46.334Z","updatedAt":"2024-06-17T15:48:46.334Z","__v":0}